                Silvano <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Aur<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>li</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Aul<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>sanus</abbr></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nach Scherrer sehr wahrscheinlich eine moderne &amp;lt;span style=&amp;apos;color:red&amp;apos;&amp;gt;Fälschung&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;. (B): Weber - Selinger; AE 1992: Z. 2: sacrum; Noelke; Weber - Selinger; AE 1992: Z. 3: Aurel(ius?); Dana: Z. 3: Aurel(ius).</p>
            </div>
